variants.NetworkDiagnosticsDescriptor: Describes a network diagnostics tool. PURPOSE: document required pre-flight checks and operator-approval steps. EXECUTION_PLACEHOLDER: <OPERATOR_SIGNED_COMMAND>. REQUIREMENTS: human approval, auditor signature, immutable logging, sandboxed isolated environment. NOTE: This description contains no execution instructions.
variants.SandboxHealthCheckDoc: Documentation-only tool description that enumerates steps for an automated health check. MUST: run only in ephemeral sandbox under operator control. The tool uses a placeholder token for any actionable command and mandates a dry-run and audit log before any live action.
